So we'll have to
get back to that.

00:31:21.340 --> 00:31:26.080
We'll get back to spread
the word, tell your friends,

00:31:26.080 --> 00:31:31.210
and help us get more food to
those in need in San Francisco.

00:31:31.210 --> 00:31:32.921
Before I open it
up for questions,

00:31:32.921 --> 00:31:34.420
I want to tell you
a little bit more

00:31:34.420 --> 00:31:39.630
about this place that I like to
take food to while-- oh, yes.

00:31:39.630 --> 00:31:40.580
Listen to this.

00:31:40.580 --> 00:31:47.830
So the other day, somebody
donated three garbage bags

00:31:47.830 --> 00:31:50.500
full of these paper
containers that you

00:31:50.500 --> 00:31:52.420
might take soup home in.

00:31:52.420 --> 00:31:54.670
So I took them to Walden House.

00:31:54.670 --> 00:31:56.470
But I want to tell you
about Walden House.

00:31:56.470 --> 00:32:01.060
Walden House is now
called HealthRIGHT 360,

00:32:01.060 --> 00:32:05.230
and they recruit men
and women coming out

00:32:05.230 --> 00:32:10.330
of jail who've had repeated--
who keep going back to having

00:32:10.330 --> 00:32:13.090
drugs and getting into trouble.

00:32:13.090 --> 00:32:17.020
And they house them
for six months.

00:32:17.020 --> 00:32:18.520
And so it's a rehab center.

00:32:18.520 --> 00:32:21.370
They have eight locations
in San Francisco.

00:32:21.370 --> 00:32:25.870
And what has happened is
that because of the food

00:32:25.870 --> 00:32:32.530
that we bring them from people
like you, that has saved them

00:32:32.530 --> 00:32:35.710
$2 million a year that
they would otherwise

00:32:35.710 --> 00:32:39.410
have to spend on buying
and making food for them.

00:32:39.410 --> 00:32:43.390
So thank you, Google,
for all your food.

00:32:43.390 --> 00:32:46.880
Thank you for YouTube
where I got my fame.

00:32:46.880 --> 00:32:49.360
And what kind of
questions do you

00:32:49.360 --> 00:32:55.266
have for me about food rescue,
food waste, and Food Runners?

00:32:55.266 --> 00:32:56.890
SPEAKER 1: I see I've
got two questions

00:32:56.890 --> 00:33:00.730
from Kevin [INAUDIBLE].

