00:33:12.940 --> 00:33:14.106
MARY RISLEY: What policies--

00:33:14.106 --> 00:33:15.130
SPEAKER 1: Yes.

00:33:15.130 --> 00:33:17.050
MARY RISLEY: --should we pass?

00:33:17.050 --> 00:33:21.772
SPEAKER 1: Yes, to lower
barriers to sharing food.

00:33:21.772 --> 00:33:23.230
MARY RISLEY: There
